meta=None content=[TextContent(type='text', text='{
  "_meta": null,
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Contents of https://www.apple.com/iphone-16/:\nGet credit toward iPhone\xa016 or iPhone\xa016\xa0Pro when you trade in an eligible\xa0smartphone.[\\*](#footnote-1) [Buy](/us/shop/goto/buy_iphone/iphone_16)You can get credit for your Android phone.[\\*](#footnote-1) [Learn more](about:/us/shop/goto/trade_in#android)\n\n6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016[3](#footnote-4) in five colors\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus[3](#footnote-4) and  \n 6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016[3](#footnote-4) in Black\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus[3](#footnote-4) and  \n 6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016[3](#footnote-4) in Ultramarine\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus[3](#footnote-4) and  \n 6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016[3](#footnote-4) in Teal\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus[3](#footnote-4) and  \n 6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016[3](#footnote-4) in Pink\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus[3](#footnote-4) and  \n 6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016[3](#footnote-4) in White\n\n6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016 in Black\n6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016 in Ultramarine\n6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016 in Teal\n6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016 in Pink\n6.1‚Äù iPhone\xa016 in White\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus in Black\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus in Ultramarine\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus in Teal\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus in Pink\n6.7‚Äù iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus in White\n\nClick and turn to explore iPhone.\nTap and turn to explore iPhone.\n\n![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-viewer/iphone/loader__2zqb16plemq6_xlarge.jpg)\n\niPhone\xa016 is built for Apple\xa0Intelligence, the personal intelligence system that helps you **write, express yourself, and get things done effortlessly**. With groundbreaking privacy protections, it gives you peace of mind that no one else can access your data ‚Äî not even Apple.\n\n* [Boost your productivity](#productivity-gallery-item-1)\n* [Express yourself visually](#expression-gallery-item-2)\n* [The start of a new era for Siri](#siri-gallery-item-3)\n\nApple\xa0Intelligence is designed to **protect your privacy at every step**. It‚Äôs integrated into the core of iPhone through on-device processing. So it‚Äôs aware of your personal information without collecting your personal information.\n\nAnd with **groundbreaking Private Cloud Compute**, Apple\xa0Intelligence can draw on larger Apple-designed server-based models, running on Apple\xa0silicon, to handle more complex requests for you while protecting your privacy.\n\n### Camera\n\n#### Take total Camera Control. Touch. Zoom. Click. Quick.\n\nNow you can take the perfect photo or video in record time. Camera\xa0Control gives you **an easier way to quickly access camera tools**. Simply slide your finger to adjust camera functions like exposure or depth of field, and toggle through each lens or use digital zoom to frame your shot ‚Äî just how you like it.\n\n[How to use Camera\xa0Control](https://support.apple.com/guide/iphone/iph0c397b154)\n\n### Visual intelligence\n\nSee the world through\n\nan entirely\xa0new\xa0lens.\n\nUse **visual intelligence**[5](#footnote-6) through Camera\xa0Control to instantly learn about objects and places you see. Just **point your iPhone\xa016 to discover more** or interact with something in front of you. Pull up a review of a restaurant you pass, search for where to buy a new item you spotted, and\xa0more.\n\n![Hand holding iPhone 16 showing results of a search using visual intelligence.](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-stories/camera-control/visual_intelligence__f0j4ykos9z6m_large.jpg)\n\n### Camera System\n\n#### New camera system. Go to great lengths to get the perfect shot.\n\nThe **versatile new iPhone\xa016 camera system** captures beautiful photos ‚Äî from up close or far away. The two-in-one 48MP Fusion camera lets you take stunning super-high-resolution images, or zoom in with the 2x optical-quality Telephoto. The Ultra Wide camera shoots extreme close-up macro photos or wider, more expansive pictures. Altogether, it‚Äôs like having **four lenses in your pocket**. And with spatial capture, you can even take photos and videos in 3D, which you can watch with Apple\xa0Vision\xa0Pro.\n\n![Raised dual camera system on iPhone 16 in Pink](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/camera-system/hero/hero_camera__bsixees3ujte_xlarge.jpg)\n\n### Ultra Wide camera\n\n#### Ultra\xa0Wide camera. Focus on the little things. And the bigger picture.\n\nThe new Ultra Wide camera with autofocus takes incredibly **sharp, detailed macro photos and videos**. You can also **frame more expansive scenes** without taking a step back. And because it has a larger aperture and bigger pixels, it can capture up to **2.6x more light** for higher image quality ‚Äî even in low light.\n\nFor compelling close-ups with exceptional detail.\n\nCapture 4x more of a scene with the Ultra\xa0Wide\xa0camera.\n\nTake spectacular high-resolution photos with the 48MP\xa0Fusion\xa0camera.\n\nZoom in on your subject with the 2x\xa0Telephoto, enabled by the 48MP\xa0Fusion camera.\n\n### Spatial Capture\n\n#### Spatial Capture. Bring a whole new dimension to your photos and videos.\n\n![The Spatial camera feature demonstrated on an iPhone 16 in White](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/camera-system/spatial/hero_spatial__gna2d6arpimq_large.png)\n\nWith its realigned cameras, iPhone\xa016 lets you take **magical photos and videos in a whole new way** using spatial capture. So you can relive those moments in immersive 3D with Apple\xa0Vision\xa0Pro.\n\n[How to take spatial photos and videos](https://support.apple.com/guide/iphone/record-spatial-videos-for-apple-vision-pro-iph6e3a6d4fe/ios)\n\n### Audio\n\n#### Audio Mix. Make your voice heard.\n\n![The Audio Mix feature demonstrated on an iPhone 16 in White  ](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/camera-system/spatial/audio__3clbnanoq82e_large.jpg)\n\nPowered by advanced intelligence and Spatial\xa0Audio capture, Audio Mix lets you **adjust the way voices sound in your videos** using three different voice options. Want to decrease background sound? Or just focus on the voices that are in frame? Simply select the mix and adjust intensity to get the sound you want after video capture.\n\n###### In-frame\n\nOnly captures the voices of the people on camera, even if people off-camera are talking during the recording.\n\n###### Studio\n\nMakes voices sound like you‚Äôre recording in a professional studio equipped with sound-dampening walls. Great for vloggers or podcasters because the recording will sound like the mic is close to the subject‚Äôs mouth, even if it‚Äôs a few feet away.\n\n###### Cinematic\n\nCaptures all of the voices around you and consolidates them toward the front of the screen ‚Äî just like sound is formatted for the movies.\n\n### Photographic Style\n\n#### Choose your Photographic Style. Change\xa0it\xa0up. Change\xa0it\xa0back.\n\n![Demonstration of how to select Photographic Styles shown on an iPhone 16 in Pink](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/photographic-styles/tone__eowv4kd87csy_large.png)\n\n#### Lock in your look.\n\nWe‚Äôve created new styles that let you **dial in your exact desired look with more advanced skin-tone rendering** and set it across your photos. And thanks to the powerful A18 chip, you can see the change in a live preview before you apply it.\n\n![Demonstration of the Gold Photographic Style](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/photographic-styles/aesthetics__56e4sx5ow9em_large.png)\n\n#### Align with your aesthetic.\n\nOur improved image pipeline also enables more creative styles, which allow you to **customize the different moods of a photo** through color.\n\n![Demonstration of the Vibrant Photographic Style and the control pad that allows you to adjust the color and tone of a photo](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/photographic-styles/megapixels__clulnpeenivm_large.png)\n\n#### Make the most of your megapixels.\n\nPersonalize every style even more with the new control pad, which makes it **easy to adjust tone and color simultaneously**. You can also use the slider to adjust the intensity of the specific colors, instead of applying a one-size-fits-all approach.\n\n#### Lock in your look.\n\nWe‚Äôve created new styles that let you **dial in your exact desired look with more advanced skin-tone rendering** and set it across your photos. And thanks to the powerful A18 chip, you can see the change in a live preview before you apply it.\n\n#### Align with your aesthetic.\n\nOur improved image pipeline also enables more creative styles, which allow you to **customize the different moods of a photo** through color.\n\n#### Make the most of your megapixels.\n\nPersonalize every style even more with the new control pad, which makes it **easy to adjust tone and color simultaneously**. You can also use the slider to adjust the intensity of the specific colors, instead of applying a one-size-fits-all approach.\n\n### A18 chip\n\n#### A18 chip. Hi. IQ.\n\nMeet A18, **custom-built for Apple\xa0Intelligence** ‚Äî and so much more. It jumps two generations ahead of the A16\xa0Bionic chip in iPhone\xa015. And it powers next-level camera features like Photographic Styles and Camera\xa0Control. All with exceptional power efficiency to extend battery life.\n\nCompare with\n\nUp to **60% faster** 6‚Äëcore CPU\n\nUp to **2x faster** 5‚Äëcore GPU\n\n### Battery\n\n#### Even longer battery\xa0life. You‚Äôll need to recharge before it\xa0will.\n\niPhone\xa016 has been designed to make room for a larger battery, which works together with A18 to deliver **a big boost in battery life**, even with so many new features. So you can game, binge, and rock on ‚Äî and on.\n\nSnap on a new MagSafe charger for **even faster wireless charging[6](#footnote-7)** ‚Äî up to 25W with a 30W power adapter or higher, enabling up to 50% charge in around 30 minutes.[7](#footnote-8)\n\nUp to **27 hours** video playback  \non iPhone\xa016\xa0Plus[8](#footnote-9)\n\nUp

meta=None content=[TextContent(type='text', text='{
  "_meta": null,
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Contents of https://www.apple.com/iphone-16/:\n than ever:**  \n over 95% recycled lithium in the battery.[15](#footnote-16)  \n 100% recycled gold in the plating of the USB-C connector and camera wires.  \n 100% recycled copper foil in the MagSafe inductive charger.\n\n![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-stories/values/fiber__chqijrl54xea_large.svg)\n\nThe packaging for iPhone\xa016 is **100% fiber based** for the first time.[16](#footnote-17) And it‚Äôs thinner, which reduces the carbon impact for shipping.[17](#footnote-18)\n\n#### Privacy\n\n![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-stories/values/apple_intelligence__e5ap8owr0466_large.svg)\n\n**Apple\xa0Intelligence protects your privacy at every step**. With on-device processing and Private Cloud Compute, no one but you can access your data ‚Äî not even Apple.\n\n![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-stories/values/apple_passwords__ggzm4p20ne6a_large.svg)\n\n**The new Passwords app** makes it even easier to access account passwords, passkeys, Wi-Fi passwords, two-factor authentication codes, and more. It stores them securely and syncs across your devices with end-to-end encryption.\n\n![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-stories/values/person_crop_circle__se6he8a5iwiu_large.svg)\n\nYou can also **control which contacts to share with an app,** rather than giving it access to all your contacts. And you can choose to share more contacts over time.\n\n#### Accessibility\n\n![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-stories/values/eye__fv7wyvyyvpyu_large.svg)\n\n**Eye Tracking** makes it possible to navigate your iPhone and use your favorite apps just by moving your eyes, thanks to the power of machine learning and the front-facing camera.\n\n![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-stories/values/apple_haptics_and_music_note__e7y375vno6qi_large.svg)\n\n**Music Haptics** matches the iPhone Taptic\xa0Engine with the rhythm of songs. So people who are deaf or hard of hearing can enjoy the Apple\xa0Music catalog in a whole new way.\n\n![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/product-stories/values/app_2_stack_3d__c50tl44mlygm_large.svg)\n\n**Vocal Shortcuts** helps people with severe atypical speech record sounds that trigger specific actions on iPhone ‚Äî set a timer, take a screenshot, scroll up and down, and more.\n\n* ### \n\n  With iPhone Mirroring, you can view your iPhone screen on your Mac and control it without picking up your phone. Continuity features also let you answer calls or messages right from your Mac. You can even copy images, video, or text from your iPhone and paste it all into a different app on your Mac. And with iCloud, you can access your files from either device.\n\n  ![Demonstration of the Continuity feature with iPhone and Mac.](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/augment/mac__dv77aki6jes2_large.jpg)\n* ### \n\n  Misplaced your iPhone? The latest Apple\xa0Watch models can show you its approximate distance and direction.[18](#footnote-19) To set up a group photo on your iPhone, join the group and use Apple\xa0Watch as a viewfinder to snap the shot. And when you take a call on your Apple\xa0Watch, just tap your iPhone to continue the conversation there.\n\n  ![Demonstration of the Continuity feature with iPhone and Apple Watch.](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/augment/watch__dpgpqni8q0a6_large.jpg)\n* ### \n\n  Set up AirPods on iPhone with just a tap. You‚Äôll love Adaptive Audio, which automatically tailors the noise control to provide the best listening experience across different environments and interactions throughout the day.\n\n  ![Demonstration of the Continuity feature with iPhone and AirPods](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/augment/airpods__chduyq53g1ci_large.jpg)\n\n* [1](#footnote-2)\n\n  Currently viewing, iPhone 16\n\n  [Buy](/us/shop/goto/buy_iphone/iphone_16)\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/apple_intelligence__e5ap8owr0466_large.png)\n\n  Apple\xa0Intelligence[2](#footnote-3)\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/chip_a18__fx20wolaltiu_large.png)\n\n  A18\xa0chip   \n  with 5‚Äëcore GPU\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/camera_button__bk5ee2syrx8i_large.png)\n\n  Camera\xa0Control\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/iphone16_camera__dpp81c0kxzue_large.png)\n\n  + Advanced dual‚Äëcamera system\n  + Advanced 48MP Fusion camera\n  + 2x Telephoto\n  + 12MP Ultra Wide camera\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/battery__b14ff4que1yq_large.png)\n\n  Up to 27 hours video playback[14](#footnote-15)\n* ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/apple_intelligence__e5ap8owr0466_large.png)\n\n  Apple\xa0Intelligence[2](#footnote-3)\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/chip_a18pro__ely8sbtg2t6q_large.png)\n\n  A18\xa0Pro\xa0chip   \n  with 6‚Äëcore GPU\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/camera_button__bk5ee2syrx8i_large.png)\n\n  Camera\xa0Control\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/iphone16pro_camera__baw0oejmgx6a_large.png)\n\n  + Pro camera system\n  + Our most advanced 48MP   \n    Fusion camera\n  + 5x Telephoto camera\n  + 48MP Ultra Wide camera\n\n  ![](/v/iphone-16/f/images/overview/contrast/icon/battery__b14ff4que1yq_large.png)\n\n  Up to 33 hours video playback[14](#footnote-15)",
      "annotations": null
    }
  ],
  "isError": false
}', annotations=None)] isError=False

